passages.name: numberOfPeople
passages.text:
<Redirect to="[[errorSize]]"
          when="livingSpace > 250"
>
</Redirect>

<Message>
  {NO_SIGNUP_NUMBER_OF_PEOPLE}
</Message>

<Response>
  <when expression="coInsured == 1">
    {EMBARK_ME_PLUS} {coInsured} {EMBARK_OTHER}
  </when>
  <when expression="coInsured > 1">
    {EMBARK_ME_PLUS} {coInsured} {EMBARK_OTHERS}
  </when>
  <when expression="coInsured == 0">
    {EMBARK_JUST_ME}
  </when>
</Response>

<NumberAction placeholder="2"
              minvalue="0"
              key="coInsured"
              next="[[{EMBARK_CONTINUE}->name]]"
              unit="{EMBARK_OTHER_PEOPLE}"
>
  <Tooltip>
    <Title>
      {NO_SIGNUP_CO_INSURED}
    </Title>
    <Description>
      {NO_SIGNUP_CO_INSURED_DESCRIPTION}
    </Description>
  </Tooltip>
</NumberAction>

passages.name: name
passages.text:
<Redirect to="[[errorNumberCoInsured]]"
          when="coInsured > 5"
>
</Redirect>

<Message>
  {NO_SIGNUP_NAME_MESSAGE}
</Message>

<TextActionSet next="[[{EMBARK_CONTINUE}->birthDate]]">
  <TextAction title="{FIRST_NAME}"
              placeholder="{EMBARK_NAME_PLACEHOLDER}"
              large="true"
              key="firstName"
  >
  </TextAction>
  <TextAction title="{EMBARK_SURNAME}"
              placeholder="{EMBARK_LAST_NAME_PLACEHOLDER}"
              large="true"
              key="lastName"
  >
  </TextAction>
</TextActionSet>

passages.name: address
passages.text:
<Message>
  {NO_SIGNUP_ADDRESS_MESSAGE}
</Message>

<Response>
  {street}, {zipCode}
</Response>

<TextActionSet next="[[{EMBARK_CONTINUE}->sizeInput]]">
  <TextAction title="Address"
              placeholder="{NO_SIGNUP_ADDRESS_PLACEHOLDER}"
              large="true"
              key="street"
  >
  </TextAction>
  <TextAction title="{NO_SIGNUP_POSTAL_CODE}"
              mask="NorwegianPostalCode"
              placeholder="{NO_SIGNUP_POSTAL_CODE_PLACEHOLDER}"
              key="zipCode"
  >
  </TextAction>
</TextActionSet>

passages.name: youthEligibilityCheck
passages.text:
<Redirect to="[[Offer]]"
          when="birthDate.Age > 30 || livingSpace > 50 || coInsured > 0"
          key="isYouth"
          value="false"
>
</Redirect>

<Redirect to="[[youth]]"
          when="true"
>
</Redirect>

passages.name: Offer
passages.text:
<Message>
  {EMBARK_OFFER_READY_MESSAGE}
</Message>

<GraphQLApi next="[[OfferSuccess]]">
  <Mutation>
    mutation CreateQuoteNorwegianHomeContents(
			$id: ID!
			$firstName: String!
			$lastName: String!
			$currentInsurer: String
			$birthDate: LocalDate!
			$street: String!
			$zipCode: String!
			$livingSpace: Int!
			$coInsured: Int!
			$isYouth: Boolean!
			$type: NorwegianHomeContentsType!
			$email: String!
		) {
		  createQuote(input: {
		  	id: $id,
			firstName: $firstName,
			lastName: $lastName,
			currentInsurer: $currentInsurer,
			birthDate: $birthDate,
			norwegianHomeContents: {
			  street: $street
			  zipCode: $zipCode
			  coInsured: $coInsured
			  isYouth: $isYouth
			  livingSpace: $livingSpace
			  type: $type
			}
			email: $email
		  }) {
			... on CompleteQuote {
			  id
			  insuranceCost {
				monthlyGross {
				  amount
				  currency
				}
				monthlyDiscount {
				  amount
				  currency
				}
				monthlyNet {
				  amount
				  currency
				}
			  }
			}
		  }
  	  	}
  </Mutation>
  <GeneratedVariable key="id"
                     type="uuid"
                     storeas="quoteId"
  >
  </GeneratedVariable>
  <Variable key="firstName"
            from="firstName"
            as="string"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Variable key="lastName"
            from="lastName"
            as="string"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Variable key="currentInsurer"
            from="currentInsurer"
            as="string"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Variable key="coInsured"
            from="coInsured"
            as="int"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Variable key="birthDate"
            from="birthDate"
            as="string"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Variable key="isYouth"
            from="isYouth"
            as="boolean"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Variable key="street"
            from="street"
            as="string"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Variable key="zipCode"
            from="zipCode"
            as="string"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Variable key="livingSpace"
            from="livingSpace"
            as="int"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Variable key="type"
            from="type"
            as="string"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Variable key="email"
            from="email"
            as="string"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Error next="[[CreateQuoteError]]">
  </Error>
  <Result key="createQuote.insuranceCost.monthlyGross.amount"
          as="monthlyGross"
  >
  </Result>
  <Result key="createQuote.insuranceCost.monthlyGross.currency"
          as="monthlyGrossCurrency"
  >
  </Result>
  <Result key="createQuote.insuranceCost.monthlyNet.amount"
          as="monthlyNet"
  >
  </Result>
  <Result key="createQuote.insuranceCost.monthlyNet.currency"
          as="monthlyNetCurrency"
  >
  </Result>
  <Result key="createQuote.insuranceCost.monthlyDiscount.amount"
          as="monthlyDiscount"
  >
  </Result>
  <Result key="createQuote.insuranceCost.monthlyDiscount.currency"
          as="monthlyDiscountCurrency"
  >
  </Result>
</GraphQLApi>
